{"tid":2514883,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［方丈］HR萬事屋，面試搵工，升職講數，你問我答","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T05:35:51.000Z","uid":141863,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"da622e6bfe021ae1f79e7b7633817e7f57bf4514","tid":2514883,"uid":141863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"完左上個，又開再一個。大家好，又係我方丈，繼續一齊討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新片: 新片: 吳靄儀陳情原文選段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NM3mHTJye70\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNM3mHTJye70&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=b7527963\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NM3mHTJye70</a><br />\n<br />\n送禮俾媽媽/ 奶奶/ 外母 方便指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IIYOlcSrDv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIIYOlcSrDv4&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=3e75e9b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IIYOlcSrDv4</a><br />\n<br />\n職場回頭草食用指南:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cN6V-nBvhZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcN6V-nBvhZM&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=a46f3c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cN6V-nBvhZM</a><br />\n<br />\n畢業立即讀碩士，真的好嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BWH1eQ5NhiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBWH1eQ5NhiU&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=246211a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BWH1eQ5NhiU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果涉及私隱，又或者冇ac，可以喺呢度問問題，我每個星期六 夜晚10:30 ，都會YouTube 直播答題目。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/442016742832236/posts/1045796175787620?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F442016742832236%2Fposts%2F1045796175787620%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=259cf30b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/442016742832236/posts/1045796175787620?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n拍片Wishlist (新)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/sZ6FNGCPufC1QJSk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FsZ6FNGCPufC1QJSk8&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=c4ea4efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/sZ6FNGCPufC1QJSk8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">如果想我幫手睇CV，可以Facebook dm - @fongcheunghr</span></strong> - 唔好用附件形式俾我啊，cap screen 先睇到的，唔好意思呀，因為輪候嘅人比較多，需時約 7-8 日，太早推會喺隊頭推到去隊尾，仲等得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">成人台shopping 野吹水就去IG: @fongcheunghr (HR野請返Facebook 排隊)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nHardcore 系, online mock in live<a href=\"https://forms.gle/9QTohQYayC5PDX4h6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F9QTohQYayC5PDX4h6&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=75a92938\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/9QTohQYayC5PDX4h6</a><br />\n有Skype既朋友可以報名，我地可以show 你簡單同埋masked version mini-CV，同埋你想做既工作簡介，我地可以一路online 做mock interview。我會拆解我既問題，點評你既答案，希望大家都會有所得。 名額只有一個月一位，要真即席，要唔怕醜，要講真話，要唔好怕係百幾人面前被點評。放心，我會用返我返工正常既語氣同問題，保證唔會係令人難堪既刁難。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">寧願最後徒勞無功，也不選擇無動於衷，５１５１翠翠翠</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8560d2c231b92debc2d93e7b89b47010cc4e637f","tid":2514883,"uid":54012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Push 麻煩方丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>正常佢都會唔俾你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054ec75bdba0fe0955a82ea4c015fa01be105835","tid":2514883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7d6b50dfe51673cc9ba739440c7dc0d525a0f9","tid"